node_6.subject: francisco lopez
node_6.description: This is francisco lopez's plan for Friday March 07: Wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am., Have breakfast and review notes for the thesis at 8:00 am., Attend a virtual seminar on AI-related economic policies at 10:00 am., Break for lunch and relax at 12:00 pm., Continue working on the thesis and gather insights from recent research papers at 1:00 pm., Attend a family gathering at the Gardner family's house at 4:05 pm., Observe and jot down inspirations for the thesis in the guest bedroom at 4:10 pm., Conclude the family gathering and head to the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 5:05 pm., Dinner and observe at the Moonlight Tavern Bar, gather materials for empirical cases at 6:00 pm., Depart from the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 8:00 pm., Review and organize notes collected throughout the day at 9:00 pm., Relax and prepare for bed at 10:30 pm., Go to bed at 11:00 pm..
